PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,FLast year's conviction of the former
OL,7,Fbishop Anthony Pierce for sexually
OL,8,Fabusing a boy in the 1980s was
OL,9,Fundoubtedly a low point in the history
OL,10,Fof the Church in Wales.
OL,12,FThe victim had remained silent for 30
OL,13,Fyears out of shame before finally
OL,14,Ftelling safeguarding officers what
OL,15,FPierce did to him in 2023.
OL,17,FBut Thursday's report seeks to answer
OL,18,Fdeeper questions about how the church
OL,19,Fhandled allegations concerning the
OL,20,Fsexual assault of a different teenager
OL,21,Fby Pierce.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,FThe conclusions make for very
OL,7,Funcomfortable reading. The reviewer
OL,8,Ffinds there were repeated missed
OL,9,Fopportunities to act by some of the
OL,10,Fmost powerful clergymen in Wales.
OL,12,FThe pattern was consistent.
OL,13,FAllegations were known at the most
OL,14,Fsenior levels in the 1990s, including
OL,15,Fwritten claims in 1999 that Pierce had
OL,16,Fadmitted abusing a 15-year-old.
OL,18,FThese were given directly to the
OL,19,FArchbishop of Wales at the time, Alwyn
OL,20,FRice Jones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,FThey were not escalated to police, not
OL,7,Fprocessed through safeguarding
OL,8,Fchannels, and not shared fully with
OL,9,Fother bishops. The reviewer describes
OL,10,Fthe handling as "wholly inappropriate
OL,11,Fand inadequate".
OL,13,FAfter Jones retired, the report
OL,14,Fdetailing the allegations was passed
OL,15,Fto his successor, Rowan Williams, who
OL,16,Flater became Archbishop of Canterbury.
OL,26,@rD@QOUsD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,FLord Williams told the review and ITV
OL,7,FNews that he did not read it and did
OL,8,Fnot appreciate that it contained
OL,9,Fmaterial amounting to a serious
OL,10,Fadmission of criminal conduct.
OL,12,FWhen he moved to London in 2002, he
OL,13,Ftook the report with his personal
OL,14,Fpapers rather than passing it to his
OL,15,Fsuccessor, something he accepts was an
OL,16,Ferror.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,FEven a decade later, hesitation
OL,7,Fremained. When the Church in Wales
OL,8,Flaunched its Historic Cases Review in
OL,9,F2009, the then Bishop of Swansea and
OL,10,FBrecon did not immediately refer the
OL,11,Fearlier allegations.
OL,13,FThe report calls that decision "not
OL,14,Fjustifiable" and also questions
OL,15,Faspects of his tone in correspondence
OL,16,Fwith Pierce. Taken together, the
OL,17,Ffindings suggest the problem lay not
OL,18,Fin individual decision-making, but in
OL,19,Fthe culture.
OL,26,@uD@`OUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
