PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,FThe Church in Wales split from the
OL,7,FChurch of England just over a century
OL,8,Fago, but operates within the same
OL,9,Ftradition. In recent years, Anglican
OL,10,Fclergy have faced repeated scrutiny
OL,11,Fover safeguarding failures in England.
OL,13,FThis report reflects familiar themes:
OL,14,Fdeference to senior clergymen and an
OL,15,Finstinct to resolve matters internally
OL,16,Fand quietly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
