FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,FIn a statement, Lord Williams said he
OL,7,Fwas "most definitely not aware of any
OL,8,Fformal, let alone criminal,
OL,9,Fallegations" relating to Anthony
OL,10,FPierce at the time of his election and
OL,11,Fhad "accepted the assurances given to
OL,12,Fthe bishops at the time of the
OL,13,Felection that there were no grounds
OL,14,Ffor anxiety".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,F"Hence, when I received the photocopy
OL,7,Fof the handwritten report, presented
OL,8,Fto me simply as historic background to
OL,9,Fthe election, I did not (given the
OL,10,Fassurances earlier provided) take this
OL,11,Fto contain any material allegations
OL,12,Fand assumed that it was also held in
OL,13,Fprovincial files (as I was given a
OL,14,Fcopy not an original)."
OL,16,FLord Williams said it was an "error"
OL,17,Fto take the report with him to
OL,18,FLambeth, south London, "rather than
OL,19,Fimmediately passing it to my successor
OL,20,For checking that he had access to it".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
