FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,FHe added: "I can only say again that I
OL,7,Fhad no indication at all of its
OL,8,Fcontaining a serious admission of
OL,9,Fguilt. But I must take responsibility
OL,10,Ffor not passing it on."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
