PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,FResponding to the review, the
OL,7,FArchbishop of Wales, Cherry Vann,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The welfare of the victims of
OL,9,Fsexual abuse must always be our
OL,10,Fparamount concern, and we offer our
OL,11,Fmost heartfelt apologies to those who
OL,12,Fhave been failed by the church in the
OL,13,Fpast.
OL,15,F"The review shows in painful detail
OL,16,Fthe missed opportunities, the harmful
OL,17,Fassumptions and the inadequate
OL,18,Fprocesses which characterised the
OL,19,FChurch's response to these allegations
OL,20,Fof abuse for far too long.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,F"This catalogue of failures can only
OL,7,Fbe a source of shame for the Church
OL,8,Fand will have caused further trauma to
OL,9,Fabuse victims and their families.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Church in Wales
OL,12,Fsaid: "The Church in Wales is
OL,13,Fdetermined to demonstrate that it is a
OL,14,Fsafe place, and that anyone coming
OL,15,Fforward will have their concerns or
OL,16,Fdisclosures taken seriously, treated
OL,17,Fwith compassion, and taken forward
OL,18,Faccording to the highest current
OL,19,Fstandards.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,F"If our people and processes have
OL,7,Ffailed victims and survivors of abuse
OL,8,Fin the past, we intend to take
OL,9,Fresponsibility for that fact and to
OL,10,Ffully apply the lessons which have
OL,11,Fbeen learned.
OL,13,F"There is no place for any form of
OL,14,Fabuse in the Church in Wales. We give
OL,15,Fthe highest priority to the care and
OL,16,Fprotection of children and vulnerable
OL,17,Fpeople in our communities. To this end
OL,18,Fwe regularly review our safeguarding
OL,19,Fprocedures and provide extensive
OL,20,Ftraining to staff and volunteers".
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
