PN,31913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772220031
OL,3,CChurch in Wales report reveals decades
OL,4,Cof abuse cover-up failures
OL,6,FThe church says it is committed to
OL,7,Ftransparency, with robust safeguarding
OL,8,Fprocesses now in place. Its leaders
OL,9,Finsist that lessons have been learned.
OL,11,FBut for many, not least the victims
OL,12,Fand their families, trust in the
OL,13,Fchurch may never fully return.
OL,15,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,16,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,17,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,18,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
